## üöÄ About This Project

OBS Stack is a comprehensive Docker-based observability and monitoring solution designed for enterprise-scale OpenWebUI deployments. Built to monitor 200+ concurrent users on AWS EC2 p3.24xlarge instances with advanced analytics, intelligent alerting, and automatic scaling capabilities.

### üéØ Key Features Covered by This License:

‚úÖ **Complete Observability Stack** - Grafana, Prometheus, Loki, cAdvisor integration
‚úÖ **User Analytics** - Real-time tracking and behavior analysis for 200+ users  
‚úÖ **GPU Monitoring** - NVIDIA GPU performance tracking optimized for p3.24xlarge
‚úÖ **Intelligent Alerting** - Proactive notifications and escalation policies
‚úÖ **Automatic Scaling** - Resource scaling based on user load and system metrics
‚úÖ **CLI Tools** - docker-logger command suite for operational excellence
‚úÖ **Windows Development Environment** - Complete testing suite for Windows 11
‚úÖ **Production Deployment Scripts** - Automated setup for Linux/EC2 environments

### üìö Documentation & Support:

- **Installation Guides** - Complete setup instructions for Windows and Linux
- **API Documentation** - REST API reference for integration
- **Dashboard Configuration** - Grafana dashboard setup and customization
- **Scaling Guides** - Resource scaling and capacity planning
- **Troubleshooting** - Common issues and resolution procedures

